==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nevertheless
<hw>Nev`er*the*less"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv. & conj.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Never</ets> + <ets>the</ets> (see <er>The</er> by that) +
<ets>less</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not the less; notwithstanding; in spite of
that; yet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>No chastening for the present seemeth to be joyous, but grievous;
<qex>nevertheless</qex>, afterward it yieldeth the peaceable fruit of
righteousness.</q> <rj><qau>Heb. xii. 11.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- However; at least; yet; still. See
<er>However</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nevew</ent>⟦br⟧
